{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14825/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14825"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:48:25"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["handheld, fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["dirty single"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman sits at desk"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14825","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14825"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1/abcbf61e-b0ba-432f-bc6a-b32715556730","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T18:57:08.175Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Set decorator Véronique Melery reveals that the presence of flowers in the House of Woodcock generated debate among the crew: “We finally agreed that the arrangements would be very natural, which went against the main rules of the time. With these visual statements, Reynolds would be ahead of his time, just as for his fashion creations” (Burg, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW75845916 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.setdecorators.org/?art=film_decor_features&amp;SHOW=SetDecor_Film_Phantom_Thread\"><u>Set Decore</u></a>”).&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1351.510748407643,271.1756070859873,553.3952030254775,480.48741042993635"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1/c59931ef-64fe-46f3-bd2e-52bdcdf5e262","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T18:57:40.108Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Cyril is seen once more at work—always holding down the fort, as it were, while Reynolds throws his tantrums. If Reynolds’s chosen tool is the sewing needle (fashion) and Alma’s the mushroom (nature), then it would seem Cyril’s is the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW106129587 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-02849.html\"><u>pen</u></a>. She takes measurements, signs checks, and conducts other business for Reynolds. This may, in another way, position her closer to Alma, who, after all, narrates the entire film. Alma and Cyril thus wield narrative control, while Reynolds toils with aesthetic matters.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14825/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:532.1999402866243,75.83001592356692,803.4636246019102,895.9335191082802"}}}]}]}]}